<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Caribbean Renaissance™ Framework | The Buckler Group</title>
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Cormorant+Garamond:wght@500;600;700&family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">

  <style>
    :root{
      --navy:#07111f;
      --midnight:#0d1a2b;
      --ink:#101828;
      --slate:#667085;
      --bone:#f7f3ea;
      --sand:#eee6d8;
      --gold:#b7904b;
      --gold-dark:#8a6a3f;
      --white:#ffffff;
      --panel:#111c2d;
      --line:rgba(183,144,75,.35);
      --soft-line:rgba(7,17,31,.12);
    }

    *{box-sizing:border-box}
    html{scroll-behavior:smooth}

    body{
      margin:0;
      font-family:"Inter", Arial, sans-serif;
      color:var(--ink);
      background:var(--bone);
      line-height:1.55;
    }

    a{color:inherit;text-decoration:none}

    .topbar{
      background:rgba(7,17,31,.96);
      color:var(--white);
      padding:17px 5vw;
      display:flex;
      align-items:center;
      justify-content:space-between;
      border-bottom:1px solid var(--line);
      position:sticky;
      top:0;
      z-index:20;
      backdrop-filter:blur(14px);
    }

    .brand{
      display:flex;
      align-items:center;
      gap:14px;
      letter-spacing:0;
      text-transform:none;
    }

    .brand .wordmark{
      font-family:Georgia, "Times New Roman", serif;
      font-size:22px;
      font-weight:500;
      letter-spacing:.01em;
      color:var(--white);
      line-height:1;
      white-space:nowrap;
    }

    nav{
      display:flex;
      gap:24px;
      font-size:12px;
      text-transform:uppercase;
      letter-spacing:.08em;
      color:rgba(255,255,255,.82);
      align-items:center;
    }

    nav a:hover{color:var(--gold)}

    .hero{
      min-height:84vh;
      background:
        radial-gradient(circle at 14% 18%, rgba(183,144,75,.18), transparent 34%),
        linear-gradient(135deg, #07111f 0%, #0d1a2b 62%, #050b14 100%);
      color:#fff;
      display:grid;
      align-items:center;
      padding:8vw 5vw;
      border-bottom:1px solid var(--line);
      position:relative;
      overflow:hidden;
    }

    .hero:before{
      content:"";
      position:absolute;
      width:520px;
      height:520px;
      border:1px solid rgba(183,144,75,.16);
      right:-170px;
      bottom:-210px;
      transform:rotate(38deg);
    }

    .hero-inner{
      max-width:1320px;
      position:relative;
      z-index:2;
    }

    .eyebrow{
      color:var(--gold);
      text-transform:uppercase;
      letter-spacing:.18em;
      font-size:12px;
      font-weight:800;
      margin-bottom:22px;
    }

    h1,h2,h3{
      font-family:Georgia, "Times New Roman", serif;
      line-height:1;
      margin:0;
      font-weight:600;
    }

    h1{
      max-width:1080px;
      font-size:clamp(54px, 8vw, 118px);
      letter-spacing:-.06em;
      line-height:.88;
    }

    .hero-subtitle{
      max-width:760px;
      margin:34px 0 0;
      color:rgba(255,255,255,.78);
      font-size:21px;
      line-height:1.7;
    }

    .hero-actions{
      display:flex;
      flex-wrap:wrap;
      gap:14px;
      margin-top:38px;
    }

    .btn{
      display:inline-flex;
      align-items:center;
      justify-content:center;
      min-width:220px;
      padding:15px 24px;
      border:1px solid var(--gold);
      text-transform:uppercase;
      letter-spacing:.13em;
      font-size:12px;
      font-weight:800;
      transition:.24s ease;
    }

    .btn.primary{
      background:var(--gold);
      color:var(--navy);
    }

    .btn.secondary{
      color:#fff;
      border-color:rgba(255,255,255,.38);
    }

    .btn.dark{
      background:var(--navy);
      color:#fff;
      border-color:var(--navy);
    }

    .btn:hover{transform:translateY(-1px)}

    section{padding:104px 5vw}

    .section-inner{
      max-width:1320px;
      margin:0 auto;
    }

    .section-head{
      max-width:1120px;
      margin-bottom:54px;
    }

    .section-head h2{
      color:var(--navy);
      font-size:clamp(46px,4.2vw,72px);
      letter-spacing:-.045em;
      line-height:1.02;
    }

    .section-head p{
      max-width:760px;
      color:#475569;
      font-size:18px;
      line-height:1.75;
      margin:22px 0 0;
    }

    .mandate-section{
      background:#fff;
      border-bottom:1px solid var(--soft-line);
    }

    .mandate-grid{
      display:grid;
      grid-template-columns:220px 1fr;
      gap:70px;
      border-top:1px solid var(--soft-line);
      padding-top:58px;
    }

    .label{
      color:var(--gold-dark);
      text-transform:uppercase;
      letter-spacing:.16em;
      font-size:11px;
      font-weight:800;
    }

    .mandate-statement{
      color:var(--navy);
      font-family:"Cormorant Garamond", Georgia, serif;
      font-size:clamp(34px, 4vw, 62px);
      line-height:1.06;
      letter-spacing:-.045em;
      margin:0;
      max-width:980px;
    }

    .diaspora-section{
      background:var(--navy);
      color:#fff;
      border-top:none;
      border-bottom:none;
    }

    .diaspora-grid{
      display:grid;
      grid-template-columns:.9fr 1.1fr;
      gap:68px;
      align-items:end;
    }

    .diaspora-grid h2{
      color:#fff;
      font-size:clamp(44px, 5.8vw, 88px);
      line-height:.9;
      letter-spacing:-.055em;
    }

    .diaspora-copy{
      color:rgba(255,255,255,.76);
      font-size:19px;
      line-height:1.78;
      margin:0;
      max-width:760px;
    }

    .diaspora-line{
      grid-column:1 / -1;
      display:grid;
      grid-template-columns:repeat(4,1fr);
      border-top:none;
      margin-top:56px;
    }

    .diaspora-line div{
      min-height:126px;
      padding:26px 24px 0 0;
      border-right:none;
    }

    .diaspora-line div:last-child{border-right:none}

    .diaspora-line strong{
      display:block;
      color:var(--gold);
      font-family:"Cormorant Garamond", Georgia, serif;
      font-size:36px;
      line-height:1;
      margin-bottom:12px;
    }

    .diaspora-line span{
      color:rgba(255,255,255,.68);
      font-size:11px;
      text-transform:uppercase;
      letter-spacing:.12em;
      font-weight:800;
      line-height:1.45;
    }

    .framework-section{
      background:var(--bone);
      border-bottom:1px solid var(--soft-line);
    }

    .pillar-index{
      border-top:1px solid var(--soft-line);
    }

    .pillar-row{
      display:grid;
      grid-template-columns:120px minmax(240px, 350px) 1fr;
      gap:34px;
      padding:28px 0;
      border-bottom:1px solid var(--soft-line);
      align-items:start;
    }

    .pillar-num{
      color:var(--gold-dark);
      font-size:11px;
      letter-spacing:.16em;
      text-transform:uppercase;
      font-weight:800;
    }

    .pillar-row h3{
      color:var(--navy);
      font-size:clamp(30px,2.4vw,36px);
      letter-spacing:-.035em;
      line-height:1;
    }

    .pillar-row p{
      color:#475569;
      margin:0;
      font-size:16px;
      line-height:1.65;
      max-width:700px;
    }

    .measurement-section{
      background:#fff;
      border-bottom:1px solid var(--soft-line);
    }

    .index-grid{
      display:grid;
      grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr);
      gap:1px;
      background:var(--soft-line);
      border:1px solid var(--soft-line);
    }

    .index-card{
      min-height:285px;
      padding:34px;
      background:#fff;
    }

    .index-card .tag{
      color:var(--gold-dark);
      text-transform:uppercase;
      letter-spacing:.14em;
      font-size:10px;
      font-weight:800;
      margin-bottom:24px;
    }

    .index-card h3{
      color:var(--navy);
      font-size:36px;
      letter-spacing:-.03em;
      margin-bottom:18px;
    }

    .index-card p{
      color:#667085;
      margin:0;
      font-size:15px;
      line-height:1.68;
    }

    .jurisdiction-section{
      background:var(--bone);
      border-bottom:1px solid var(--soft-line);
    }

    .jurisdiction-grid{
      display:grid;
      grid-template-columns:repeat(4,1fr);
      border-top:1px solid var(--soft-line);
      border-left:1px solid var(--soft-line);
    }

    .jurisdiction-card{
      min-height:210px;
      background:#fff;
      padding:26px;
      border-right:1px solid var(--soft-line);
      border-bottom:1px solid var(--soft-line);
    }

    .jurisdiction-card span{
      display:block;
      color:var(--gold-dark);
      text-transform:uppercase;
      letter-spacing:.14em;
      font-size:10px;
      font-weight:800;
      margin-bottom:18px;
    }

    .jurisdiction-card strong{
      display:block;
      color:var(--navy);
      font-family:"Cormorant Garamond", Georgia, serif;
      font-size:32px;
      line-height:1;
      letter-spacing:-.03em;
      margin-bottom:14px;
    }

    .jurisdiction-card p{
      color:#667085;
      margin:0;
      font-size:14px;
      line-height:1.6;
    }

    .architecture-section{
      background:#fff;
      border-bottom:1px solid var(--soft-line);
    }

    .architecture-stack{
      border-top:1px solid var(--soft-line);
    }

    .architecture-row{
      display:grid;
      grid-template-columns:260px 1fr 1.1fr;
      gap:34px;
      padding:34px 0;
      border-bottom:1px solid var(--soft-line);
      align-items:start;
    }

    .architecture-row span{
      color:var(--gold-dark);
      text-transform:uppercase;
      letter-spacing:.14em;
      font-size:10px;
      font-weight:800;
    }

    .architecture-row h3{
      color:var(--navy);
      font-size:40px;
      letter-spacing:-.035em;
    }

    .architecture-row p{
      color:#667085;
      margin:0;
      font-size:15px;
      line-height:1.7;
      max-width:700px;
    }

    .cta-band{
      background:linear-gradient(90deg, var(--navy), #13243b);
      color:#fff;
      padding:72px 5vw;
    }

    .cta-inner{
      max-width:1320px;
      margin:0 auto;
      display:flex;
      justify-content:space-between;
      gap:36px;
      align-items:center;
    }

    .cta-band h2{
      color:#fff;
      font-size:clamp(34px, 4vw, 58px);
      letter-spacing:-.04em;
      max-width:760px;
    }

    footer{
      background:#050b14;
      color:rgba(255,255,255,.68);
      padding:42px 5vw;
      display:flex;
      justify-content:space-between;
      gap:24px;
      flex-wrap:wrap;
      font-size:13px;
    }

    
    /* Institutional refinements */
    .section-head{
      max-width:1180px;
    }
    .section-head h2{
      word-break:normal;
      overflow-wrap:normal;
      max-width:980px;
    }
    .pillar-row{
      grid-template-columns:110px 320px 1fr;
    }
    .diaspora-grid{
      align-items:center;
    }
    .diaspora-copy{
      font-size:20px;
    }
    .mandate-statement{
      font-family:Georgia,"Times New Roman",serif;
      font-weight:400;
      letter-spacing:-.03em;
    }
    .architecture-row h3,
    .index-card h3,
    .jurisdiction-card strong,
    .pillar-row h3{
      font-family:Georgia,"Times New Roman",serif;
      font-weight:400;
    }

    @media(max-width:1050px){
      nav{display:none}
      .mandate-grid,
      .diaspora-grid,
      .architecture-row,
      .cta-inner{
        grid-template-columns:1fr;
        display:grid;
      }
      .index-grid,
      .jurisdiction-grid{
        grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;
      }
      .pillar-row{
        grid-template-columns:1fr;
        gap:14px;
      }
      .diaspora-line{
        grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;
      }
    }

    @media(max-width:700px){
      .brand .wordmark{font-size:18px}
      .hero{min-height:auto;padding:92px 5vw}
      section{padding:76px 5vw}
      .index-grid,
      .jurisdiction-grid,
      .diaspora-line{
        grid-template-columns:1fr;
      }
      .diaspora-line div{
        border-right:none;
        border-bottom:none;
      }
      .diaspora-line div:last-child{border-bottom:none}
      .hero-actions{display:grid}
      .btn{width:100%}
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>
  <header class="topbar">
    <a class="brand" href="index.html" aria-label="The Buckler Group home">
      <span class="wordmark">The Buckler Group</span>
    </a>
    <nav>
      <a href="index.html">Main Site</a>
      <a href="#mandate">Mandate</a>
      <a href="#diaspora">Diaspora Return</a>
      <a href="#framework">Framework</a>
      <a href="charter-membership.html">EXODUS™</a>
    </nav>
  </header>

  <main>
    <section class="hero">
      <div class="hero-inner">
        <div class="eyebrow">The Caribbean Renaissance™ Framework</div>
        <h1>Many Islands.<br>One Civilization.</h1>
        <p class="hero-subtitle">
          An institutional framework for organizing Caribbean capital, development,
          leadership, culture, resilience, and diaspora participation.
        </p>
</div>
    </section>

    <section class="mandate-section" id="mandate">
      <div class="section-inner">
        <div class="mandate-grid">
          <div class="label">Mandate</div>
          <p class="mandate-statement">
            The Caribbean Renaissance™ exists to organize the conditions under which
            Caribbean opportunity can compound: clearer policy, stronger institutions,
            disciplined entitlement pathways, investable projects, coordinated leadership,
            and productive diaspora participation.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="diaspora-section" id="diaspora">
      <div class="section-inner">
        <div class="diaspora-grid">
          <div>
            <div class="eyebrow">Diaspora Return</div>
            <h2>From travel to participation.</h2>
          </div>
          <p class="diaspora-copy">
            The diaspora is not merely a visitor segment. It is a long-horizon economic,
            cultural, intellectual, and institutional asset. When coordinated, diaspora travel
            can convert into investment, enterprise formation, real estate activity,
            knowledge transfer, philanthropy, and national participation.
          </p>

          <div class="diaspora-line">
            <div><strong>Travel</strong><span>Recurring destination engagement</span></div>
            <div><strong>Capital</strong><span>Investment, enterprise, real estate, remittances</span></div>
            <div><strong>Talent</strong><span>Knowledge transfer and leadership networks</span></div>
            <div><strong>Legacy</strong><span>Institutional stewardship across generations</span></div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="framework-section" id="framework">
      <div class="section-inner">
        <div class="section-head">
          <div class="eyebrow">Framework Pillars</div>
          <h2>Nine pillars for regional transformation.</h2>
          <p>
            The pillars provide a shared operating language for policy, capital,
            convening, jurisdiction intelligence, and investment strategy.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="pillar-index">
          <div class="pillar-row"><div class="pillar-num">Pillar 01</div><h3>Capital & Investment</h3><p>Mobilize institutional, private, and diaspora capital into bankable regional opportunities.</p></div>
          <div class="pillar-row"><div class="pillar-num">Pillar 02</div><h3>Real Estate & Infrastructure</h3><p>Build entitlement clarity, resilient districts, mixed-use development, housing, ports, airports, and civic infrastructure.</p></div>
          <div class="pillar-row"><div class="pillar-num">Pillar 03</div><h3>Tourism & Hospitality</h3><p>Reposition tourism as a platform for enterprise formation, asset creation, and destination competitiveness.</p></div>
          <div class="pillar-row"><div class="pillar-num">Pillar 04</div><h3>Food & Culinary</h3><p>Elevate cuisine, agriculture, food exports, culinary tourism, and cultural diplomacy as economic infrastructure.</p></div>
          <div class="pillar-row"><div class="pillar-num">Pillar 05</div><h3>Sports & Human Performance</h3><p>Use sport to advance tourism, youth development, athlete pathways, health, and national brand value.</p></div>
          <div class="pillar-row"><div class="pillar-num">Pillar 06</div><h3>Culture & Creative Economy</h3><p>Convert music, festivals, film, fashion, heritage, and creative industries into exportable global influence.</p></div>
          <div class="pillar-row"><div class="pillar-num">Pillar 07</div><h3>Education & Leadership</h3><p>Build leadership capacity, applied research, workforce systems, and institutional competence.</p></div>
          <div class="pillar-row"><div class="pillar-num">Pillar 08</div><h3>Technology & Innovation</h3><p>Accelerate productivity through AI, digital government, FinTech, PropTech, AgTech, and data systems.</p></div>
          <div class="pillar-row"><div class="pillar-num">Pillar 09</div><h3>Sustainability & Climate Resilience</h3><p>Protect natural capital through blue economy strategy, renewable energy, coastal resilience, and climate adaptation.</p></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="measurement-section" id="indices">
      <div class="section-inner">
        <div class="section-head">
          <div class="eyebrow">Measurement Architecture</div>
          <h2>What gets measured can be organized.</h2>
          <p>
            The Framework is supported by three practical indices for evaluating regional readiness,
            diaspora impact, and investable jurisdiction capacity.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="index-grid">
          <article class="index-card">
            <div class="tag">Regional</div>
            <h3>Caribbean Renaissance Index™</h3>
            <p>A composite measure of regional progress across capital, infrastructure, governance, culture, leadership, and resilience.</p>
          </article>
          <article class="index-card">
            <div class="tag">Diaspora</div>
            <h3>Diaspora Return Index™</h3>
            <p>A measure of value created through coordinated diaspora travel, investment, knowledge transfer, enterprise, and national participation.</p>
          </article>
          <article class="index-card">
            <div class="tag">Investment</div>
            <h3>Investment Readiness Index™</h3>
            <p>A jurisdiction scorecard for entitlement clarity, investor access, infrastructure capacity, policy stability, and execution readiness.</p>
          </article>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="jurisdiction-section">
      <div class="section-inner">
        <div class="section-head">
          <div class="eyebrow">Jurisdiction Intelligence</div>
          <h2>Regional vision requires country-level discipline.</h2>
          <p>
            Each jurisdiction requires its own investment narrative, entitlement pathway,
            stakeholder map, infrastructure priorities, and diaspora strategy.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="jurisdiction-grid">
          <article class="jurisdiction-card"><span>Market Readiness</span><strong>Policy</strong><p>Investment promotion, permitting, PPP rules, fiscal clarity, and regulatory confidence.</p></article>
          <article class="jurisdiction-card"><span>Land & Entitlement</span><strong>Real Estate</strong><p>Zoning, title, site control, coastal setbacks, EIA requirements, and development approvals.</p></article>
          <article class="jurisdiction-card"><span>Capital Formation</span><strong>Investment</strong><p>Project pipeline, sponsor credibility, incentives, development finance, and institutional capital access.</p></article>
          <article class="jurisdiction-card"><span>Public Trust</span><strong>Execution</strong><p>Stakeholder coordination, transparency, local participation, and long-horizon governance.</p></article>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="architecture-section">
      <div class="section-inner">
        <div class="section-head">
          <div class="eyebrow">Platform Architecture</div>
          <h2>The institutional hierarchy.</h2>
          <p>
            The Framework clarifies how The Buckler Group, EXODUS™, and the Caribbean Renaissance™
            operate as one ecosystem with distinct roles.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="architecture-stack">
          <div class="architecture-row">
            <span>Institutional Home</span>
            <h3>The Buckler Group</h3>
            <p>Strategic advisory, policy, investment positioning, entitlement intelligence, and implementation strategy.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="architecture-row">
            <span>Participation Platform</span>
            <h3>EXODUS™</h3>
            <p>Executive convening, charter participation, investor dialogue, jurisdiction briefings, and strategic access.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="architecture-row">
            <span>Regional Framework</span>
            <h3>Caribbean Renaissance™</h3>
            <p>The civilizational thesis organizing policy, capital, culture, leadership, resilience, and diaspora participation.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="cta-band">
      <div class="cta-inner">
        <h2>Participate in the Caribbean Renaissance™ through EXODUS™.</h2>
        <div class="hero-actions">
          <a href="charter-membership.html" class="btn primary">Request Participation</a>
          <a href="index.html" class="btn secondary">Return to TBG</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>

  <footer>
    <div>© 2026 The Buckler Group. All rights reserved.</div>
    <div>Caribbean Renaissance™ Framework · Powered by EXODUS™</div>
  </footer>
</body>
</html>
